      "title": "200 lakh car sacrificed to the fire monster",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kataragama Police say that a luxury car coming from Wattala to Kataragama caught fire suddenly at Tammananawa Menikwala Junction.",
        "The driver told the police that this car is worth around 210 lakh rupees.",
        "A resident of Wattala, Ederamulla, railway station along with his friend was coming to Kataragama via Mattala Lunugamwehera on the expressway at around 11:00 pm when the car caught fire on the south side and stopped the car and jumped out with his friend. The Kataragama police have stated that it was not."
      ],
